---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import LeadForm from "../../components/LeadForm.astro";
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import RelatedServices from '../../components/RelatedServices.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Weight Management Clinic | KM Wellness Center | El Paso, TX',
  description:
    'Join our weight management clinic for expert guidance and personalized plans to help you achieve your weight loss goals and improve health.',
};
---
<BaseLayout {...seo}>
  <Breadcrumbs crumbs={[{ name: 'Home', href: '/' }, { name: 'Services', href: '/services/' }, { name: 'Weight Management', href: '/services/weight-management/' }]} />
  <h1>Weight Management Clinic in El Paso</h1>

  <p>
    Struggling with weight can affect more than just your appearance — it can impact your energy,
    confidence, and overall health. At KM Wellness Center, we are a trusted weight management clinic in
    El Paso offering safe, medically guided solutions for long-term results. Our approach is built on
    science, support, and sustainable change.
  </p>

  <section>
    <h2>Medical Weight Loss El Paso Residents Can Rely On</h2>
    <p>
      We specialize in medical weight loss in El Paso, helping patients lose weight under the care of
      experienced medical professionals. Our plans are clinically designed and supervised to improve
      your health from the inside out, while addressing related conditions like high blood pressure,
      diabetes, or joint pain.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Prescription Weight Loss Programs That Work</h2>
    <p>
      We offer prescription weight loss programs for patients who qualify. These FDA-approved
      medications can help reduce hunger, boost metabolism, and make it easier to stick to a healthier
      lifestyle, with regular check-ins and progress tracking.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Clinically Supervised Weight Loss</h2>
    <p>
      Our program includes thorough medical evaluations, lab work when needed, and one-on-one
      coaching. This structured approach keeps your progress safe and steady while minimizing side
      effects and setbacks.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Doctor Supervised, Non-Surgical Solutions</h2>
    <p>
      Working with a healthcare provider means you're never alone in your journey. We believe in
      healthy weight loss solutions that work with your body — non-invasive treatments designed to
      help you lose weight without surgery or extreme measures, with personalized plans for every
      body.
    </p>
    <p><a href="/contact-us/">Make an appointment</a></p>
  </section>

  <RelatedServices current="/services/weight-management/" />

  <LeadForm source="weight-management" service="Weight Loss Program" />
</BaseLayout>
